          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "EXTB",
                "STTA",
                "EDEG",
                "MOSEP",
                "BCINT"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "The Energy Degradation in the Stack was Calculated",
                "According to C.F.Williamson Et Al.,Cea-R3042(1966).",
                "Cu-Monitor Foils of 12.57 Mg/Cm**2 were Used.",
                "The Integrated Beam Charge Determined by Monitoring",
                "Agreed Within 1% with the Value Obtained with the",
                "Faraday Cup.",
                "Typical Irradiations Lasted 200 Sec at 0.5 Microamps."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Stacks of Self-Supporting Polystyrene Films in Which",
                "1.05+-0.01 Mg/Cm**2 Enriched Te-124 Powder were",
                "Uniformly Suspended, Interspersed with Al and Cu Beam",
                "Degrader Foils. The Te-Concentration in Each Target",
                "Was Determined at the Conclusion of the Experiment",
                "By X-Ray Fluorescence Spectrometry. Separate Sets",
                "Of Measurements were Performed with Targets Having",
                "The Following Differing Isotopic Compositions (IN %)",
                "      1.Te-120 < 0.002, Te-122 < 0.003, Te-123  0.006,",
                "Te-124 99.87, Te-125  0.095,  Te-126  0.020,  Te-128 <",
                "0.010, Te-130 < 0.008.  Other Impurities were < 1%.",
                "      2.Te-120 < 0.02, Te-122 0.49, Te-123 0.11,",
                "Te-124 91.86, Te-125 3.17, Te-126 1.81, Te-128 1.55,",
                "Te-130 1.05. Other Impurities were Less Than 1%."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GELI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "The Dead-Time Losses were Always Less Than 10%."
              ]
            }
          ],
